WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:16.540
Ingredients:
3 cups Sticky Rice, (Soaked overnight in water)
2 cups Adzuki Bean
2 pieces Dried Madarin Peel
1 cup Brown Sugar
8 cups Water
Bamboo leaves &amp; String

00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:43.480
Adzuki beans are some of the most nutritious beans.are a rich source of iron that increases your energy levels also known to reduce the effects of asthma.

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:51.060
2 pieces Dried Mandarin Peel, (Washed and Soaked).

00:00:52.000 --> 00:01:01.800
Add 2 cups adzuki beans in the pot, thoroughly wash and drain beans.

00:01:03.720 --> 00:01:11.560
then pour 5 cup water and bring to a boil over medium high heat and cook for an hour.

00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:23.700
Add another 3 cups of water, turn it to medium heat and cook for an hour. Add 2 pieces mandarin peel &amp; leave it until the beans are soft.

00:01:25.580 --> 00:01:35.620
Add 1 cup brown sugar, (You can adjust your sweetness level reaches the desired) Stir until well combined. Set aside to cool completely.

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:44.080
Add the cooked adzuki bean to a blender and blend until smooth.

00:01:44.460 --> 00:01:52.860
If you prefer something a bites that tastes, I recommend you add 3-5 tbsps unblended cooked adzuki beans to the smooth paste.

00:01:53.080 --> 00:01:57.420
Place the adzuki bean paste into a large bowl.
Sweet red bean paste filling are turned out perfectly.

00:02:49.640 --> 00:02:58.140
Add the rice dumplings in the deep pot, and add water, Cook for an hour. Serve and Happy Dragon Boat Festival!

